    public class ContextAnnotationAutowireCandidateResolver
extends org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.QualifierAnnotationAutowireCandidateResolver
    Complete implementation of the AutowireCandidateResolver strategy interface, providing support for qualifier annotations as well as for lazy resolution driven by the Lazy annotation in the context.annotation package.
    从以下版本开始:
    4.0

      • getLazyResolutionProxyIfNecessary

        @Nullable
public java.lang.Object getLazyResolutionProxyIfNecessary(org.springframework.beans.factory.config.DependencyDescriptor descriptor,
                                                                    @Nullable
                                                                    java.lang.String beanName)
        从接口复制的说明: org.springframework.beans.factory.support.AutowireCandidateResolver
        Build a proxy for lazy resolution of the actual dependency target, if demanded by the injection point.

        The default implementation simply returns null.

        指定者:
        getLazyResolutionProxyIfNecessary 在接口中 org.springframework.beans.factory.support.AutowireCandidateResolver
        覆盖:
        getLazyResolutionProxyIfNecessary 在类中 org.springframework.beans.factory.support.SimpleAutowireCandidateResolver
        参数:
        descriptor - the descriptor for the target method parameter or field
        beanName - the name of the bean that contains the injection point
        返回:
        the lazy resolution proxy for the actual dependency target, or null if straight resolution is to be performed
